videos.description: Zion Williamson shows off the range as he hits a 3-pointer for his first points as a Blue Devil.
videos.headline: Zion knocks down early 3-ball for Duke

videos.description: R.J. Barrett runs the floor and finishes with a two-handed dunk to put Duke up big early on Kentucky.
videos.headline: Barrett throws down fast-break slam

videos.description: Zion Williamson blows by the defender and finishes with a layup through contact.
videos.headline: Zion drives the lane for and-1 bucket

videos.description: Zion Williamson shows no mercy on the rim as he throws down a fast-break dunk.
videos.headline: Zion explodes for two-handed jam

videos.description: R.J. Barrett leads the way for Duke as he knocks down an open 3-pointer to extend its lead.
videos.headline: Barrett hits 3-pointer, leads Duke in scoring

videos.description: R.J. Barrett drives the lane and throws an alley-oop to Marques Bolden who finishes with two hands.
videos.headline: Bolden throws down lob from Barrett

videos.description: Tre Jones comes up with the steal and misses the layup, but Zion Williamson is there to clean it up.
videos.headline: Zion rises for putback dunk

videos.description: Zion Williamson comes up with a block on defense that leads to an and-1 layup for R.J. Barrett.
videos.headline: Zion blocks, runs the floor and drops dime to Barrett

videos.description: Zion Williamson blows past the Kentucky defense for a one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Zion goes up for one-handed dunk

videos.description: Zion Williamson says he loves dunking because of the energy it brings to the entire Duke team.
videos.headline: Zion calls dunks 'energy boosters' for Duke

videos.description: In his debut with the Blue Devils, RJ Barrett records 33 points as Duke beats Kentucky by 34.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Barrett’s 33 points fuel Duke’s blowout win vs. Kentucky) 2018/11/06 ESHEET SOT FULL

videos.headline: Barrett's 33 points fuel Duke's blowout win vs. Kentucky.

videos.description: In response to if the Blue Devils are playing like a March team, Mike Krzyzewski says "they're freshman, what the hell do they know."

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Presser (Coach K, Zion laugh off playing like a March team) 2018/11/6

videos.headline: Coach K, Zion laugh off playing like a March team
